storm petrel
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(aka Jesus Christ bird, skipjack, dancing dolly, (all from its apparent ability to `walk' on water), =takahikaremoana ) a very small black seabird with a white rump, which follows ships and whose appearance was thought to announce a coming storm.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also storm bird
